{"tid":2256373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國安顧問：將在西太平洋部署海岸衛隊巡邏艇抗衡中國","createTime":"2020-10-24T09:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T10:50:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9817f12279f14376571bd1f72106faf4d2fd9db1","tid":2256373,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556485-20201024.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556485-20201024.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=5c1b1ac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556485-20201024.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c01ffbb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556485-20201024.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問奧布萊恩說，美國海岸防衛隊將在西太平洋部署新一代快速反應巡邏艇，執行海上安全任務，抗衡中國的活動。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩在聲明中，形容美國是太平洋大國，指中國在印太地區其他國家的專屬經濟海域「非法捕魚」，又「騷擾」其他船隻作業，威脅美國及太平洋鄰國的主權，危害區域安全。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩沒有詳細說明，美國巡邏艇將部署在何處及部署數目，強調美國的行動對於抗衡中國「破壞穩定及惡意行動」至關重要，又說美國海岸防衛隊加強在印太地區的存在，確保美國將繼續是區內首選的海上盟友。<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，美國海岸防衛隊計劃在下一個財政年度，評估在南太平洋美屬薩摩亞部署快速反應巡邏艇的可能。"},{"pid":"8e332b46187b7c90bf46ec245fc238c539629eec","tid":2256373,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備變敵對國"},{"pid":"486c1be8ef2a70274e7cdd918b5e256f2781d218","tid":2256373,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c58368b817fe48a77d6035ff3d41bfba6c1ddc","tid":2256373,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e332b46187b7c90bf46ec245fc238c539629eec","tid":2256373,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備變敵對國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c84c3d18e25bc8cee36a3aa78590f32576acfc","tid":2256373,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"放心 拜登上台會制止"}]}